<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Nexus -&gt; Shadowhaven:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
From the center of the Nexus, head east.  If you don't know which way east is, head to the NK spire.  If you still can't find your way, click the little button named &quot;Sense Heading&quot; about 1000 times, or just buy a compass.  ;-)<br>
<br>
Above the Antonica Spire there should be a a small room with a tile in the center of it.  Step on the tile.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Shadowhaven -&gt; Nexus:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
You'll end up in the center of the spires in the water in Shadowhaven.  Carefully (without falling into the water if you're a non-gating short race) walk to the platform with a tile suspended over the water.<br>
<br>
Ride the teleporter back to the Center of the Nexus.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Banking</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
There are many banks in Shadowhaven and Echo Caverns you can use instead of the Crowded Bazaar banks. <p>--Captain Antoin Nolouj
